00:11:43.190 --> 00:11:46.230
We are all citizens
of the planet Earth.

00:11:46.230 --> 00:11:49.110
And so we celebrate these titles

00:11:49.110 --> 00:11:51.890
and we congratulate their
authors and illustrators.

00:11:51.890 --> 00:11:54.510
Thank you.

